'''Refuge City''' was a city established by a [[Caamasi Remnant]] community on [[Caamas/Legends|Caamas]] during the time of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. In a large crater 70 miles south of the city was a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] salvage operation, [[Bothan Debris, Incorporated]], which worked to recover any equipment or materials that might have survived the destruction of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]].

